* --------------------------------------
* requirements
* --------------------------------------
- PHP5+
- ImageMagick (convert command)

* --------------------------------------
* setup
* --------------------------------------
% cd image
% wget http://example.com/photo.gif
% mv photo.gif image.gif
% vi convert.sh
(modify output size and number of colors)

% cd ../
% vi index.html
(make links to the appropriate pages corresponding to the convert.sh)

* --------------------------------------
* usage
* --------------------------------------
access index.html via smartphone or tablet device.



Enjoy!
